description: A Face Recognition System using Django is a web-based application that leverages machine learning to detect and recognize human faces from images or video streams. This system integrates Django as the backend framework and uses OpenCV and deep learning models (e.g., FaceNet, Dlib, or OpenCVs Haar cascades) for facial recognition.
